{"type": "article", "id": 19978, "title": "我们挑了Tumblr 年度回顾里最有特点的那部分，请勿使用流量观看", "description": "这个网站有毒", "date": "2015-12-30T20:02:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 5340, "name": "2015"}, {"id": 87, "name": "Tumblr"}], "category": 18, "author": 103970, "comment_count": 31, "praise_count": 800, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607172047Yg4zWNJqFHlcTw1E.png", "contents": "\n\n<div>\r\n\t作为全球最大的轻博客网站，雅虎旗下的 Tumblr（俗称汤不热）拥有 4.2 亿用户，支持各种图文、GIF，因此也往往成为各种网络热门图的发祥地。\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t和 Instagram 和 Twitter 这样的更注重图片／文字的社交平台不同，Tumblr 因为内容的发布更自由，所以上面的东西五花八门什么都有，最近它们也发布了网站的<a href=\"http://yearinreview.tumblr.com/2015\" target=\"_blank\">年终盘点</a>，光是分类就有几十种，动图多到可对眼球造成成吨伤害。\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t我们挑选了一些非常具有 Tumblr 特色的部分，请连上 Wi-Fi 再欣赏。\r\n</div>\r\n<h4>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://yearinreview.tumblr.com/post/134753922262/most-reblogged-memes\" target=\"_blank\"> </a><a href=\"http://yearinreview.tumblr.com/post/134753922262/most-reblogged-memes\" target=\"_blank\">转发最多的魔性元素我们都认识</a> \r\n</h4>\r\n<p>\r\n\t排名第一的这位大家应该很熟悉，它在微博上也很火。全名是 Pepe the Forg，一般叫悲伤蛙。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607172029Y20KGUJCeF7ho5js.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.51574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t通常可用来表达“生无可恋”和“科科”两种情绪。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060717203027OD0zrxVBcXLHdy.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.618\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607172030G7YR1Z6luCSnzgvx.jpg\" title=\"设计师都很爱它，大概是因为设计师的内心都很苦\" alt=\"设计师都很爱它，大概是因为设计师的内心都很苦\" data-ratio=\"0.51574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>设计师都很爱它，大概是因为设计师的内心都很苦</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://yearinreview.tumblr.com/tagged/gif+art\" target=\"_blank\">今年最棒的 GIF 艺术……</a> \r\n</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607172032DPXNSkbfLgy7jRKs.gif\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.2875\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t@mspenale\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607172033WAwmQzGbi7rTF9hV.gif\" title=\"@protobacillus\" alt=\"@protobacillus\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\"><span>@protobacillus</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607172035ScRz8KF7wGrTXeZn.gif\" title=\"@themiddleofsomecalibrations\" alt=\"@themiddleofsomecalibrations\" data-ratio=\"0.64814815\" data-format=\"gif\"><span>@themiddleofsomecalibrations</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607172036bNfHEF0D3dc5Prus.gif\" title=\"@kiszkiloszki\" alt=\"@kiszkiloszki\" data-ratio=\"1.01202405\" data-format=\"gif\"><span>@kiszkiloszki</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071720371W0iwjklAvCqnZtP.gif\" title=\"@thomrugo\" alt=\"@thomrugo\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\"><span>@thomrugo</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607172037BVzY5wGo74FpPdEk.gif\" title=\"@sanshu-seiso\" alt=\"@sanshu-seiso\" data-ratio=\"0.70740741\" data-format=\"gif\"><span>@sanshu-seiso</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t风景照也是会动的……\r\n</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071720382MOG46uPB3LAIytw.gif\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.562\" data-format=\"gif\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t这套手绘风景画徽章获得了 28 万条评论\r\n</h4>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607172040aQzMNboO1hX29DSd.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607172040QjdEtFWpXsanrvI8.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607172041jrnlSXsVJadx9WYO.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.94814815\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t所有今年汤不热上好看的风景照片<strong><a href=\"http://yearinreview.tumblr.com/tagged/landscape\" target=\"_blank\">戳这里</a></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\t还有那些靠在 Tumblr 连载今年出了书的\r\n</h4>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607172041m3y0K9lISXpGvDPf.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://knockknockstuff.com/product/calm-the-fck-down/\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Calm the F*</em><em>c</em><em>k</em> <em>D</em><em>o</em><em>w</em><em>n</em></a><em>：</em><em>一</em><em>本不靠谱的教育指南</em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em></em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607172042dxG5jRIO4y7f9eXA.jpg\" title=\"Life.love.beauty：一本摄影集\" alt=\"Life.love.beauty：一本摄影集\" data-ratio=\"1.28534704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><a href=\"http://us.macmillan.com/books/9781250065704\" target=\"_blank\">Life.love.beauty</a>：一本个人摄影集</span></em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em></em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607172042VIlOYZszx6edEgc1.jpg\" title=\"TEXTASTROPHE: A COLLECTION OF HILARIOUSLY CATASTROPHIC TEXT PRANKS：搞笑短信集子\" alt=\"TEXTASTROPHE: A COLLECTION OF HILARIOUSLY CATASTROPHIC TEXT PRANKS：搞笑短信集子\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><a href=\"http://us.macmillan.com/textastropheacollectionofhilariouslycatastrophictextpranks/mattandrews\" target=\"_blank\">TEXTASTROPHE</a>：搞笑短信集子</span></em> \r\n</p>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t今年 Tumblr 上那些好看的男人们\r\n</h4>\r\n<p>\r\n\t大家基本上已经看腻了那些白人男模……\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071720444zVPK6vqIcnYmElk.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.73707533\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060717204485Tcu379Q0tH2ozF.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.18759232\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607172044YtCHqGysi1OLuRZW.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607172045rJvmHS542cDNdCP1.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607172045yLg3cTK0OlEBkow9.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.56806931\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t以及，今年的 Tumblr 鸡汤大全\r\n</h4>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607172046sWCbA68PegK3U7Xd.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.666\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t需要常备一些英文鸡汤用来发朋友圈的朋友请<strong><a href=\"http://yearinreview.tumblr.com/tagged/wisdom\" target=\"_blank\">戳这里</a></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\t最后，这里有 81 个推荐关注 \r\n</h4>\r\n<p>\r\n\tTumblr 官方选出的今年平台上的活跃账号，基本上先关注它们就没错啦：\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<ol style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<li>\r\n\t\t<a href=\"http://topherchris.tumblr.com/\">topherchris</a> \r\n\t</li>\r\n\t<li>\r\n\t\t<a href=\"http://laughingsquid.tumblr.com/\">Laug